 "text": "\n\nFix: \n\n\u003cvuxml xmlns=\"http://www.vuxml.org/apps/vuxml-1\"\u003e\n   \u003cvuln vid=\"af713140-526e-401c-8e98-a5dd4a76e912\"\u003e\n     \u003ctopic\u003etptest -- TPTEST pwd Remote Stack Buffer Overflow\u003c/topic\u003e\n     \u003caffects\u003e\n       \u003cpackage\u003e\n         \u003cname\u003etptest\u003c/name\u003e\n         \u003crange\u003e\u003ceq\u003e3.1.7\u003c/eq\u003e\u003c/range\u003e\n       \u003c/package\u003e\n     \u003c/affects\u003e\n     \u003cdescription\u003e\n       \u003cbody xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"\u003e\n         \u003cp\u003eSecurityFocus reports:\u003c/p\u003e\n         \u003cblockquote cite=\"http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/33785\"\u003e\n           \u003cp\u003eTPTEST is prone to a remote stack-based buffer-overflow vulnerability.\n\nAn attacker can exploit this issue to execute arbitrary code within the context of the affected application. Failed exploit attempts will result in a denial-of-service condition.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n         \u003c/blockquote\u003e\n       \u003c/body\u003e\n     \u003c/description\u003e\n     \u003creferences\u003e\n      \u003cbid\u003e33785\u003c/bid\u003e\n      \u003curl\u003ehttp://www.securityfocus.com/bid/33785\u003c/url\u003e\n     \u003c/references\u003e\n     \u003cdates\u003e\n       \u003cdiscovery\u003e2009-02-16\u003c/discovery\u003e\n       \u003centry\u003e2009-02-21\u003c/entry\u003e\n     \u003c/dates\u003e\n   \u003c/vuln\u003e"
